commitResults.messageTitle: Added Greeting, echo and exit feature
Added add and list feature. Encapsulated task.
Added marking as done feature. Changed naming convention to be the same as the "partial solution given".
Added ToDos, Events and Deadlines features. Made some other minor changes (e.g. creating function to draw line).
Moved the initialisation of scanner object outside the while-loop so that it doesn't get reinitialised everytime a new input is passed in.
Modified "input.txt" by adding some input test cases. Modified "EXPECTED.txt" by adding expected result for the the test case inputs.

Added new line to the bottom of the text files.
Added exception handling feature for making sure users type a description for todo and making sure that user do not type any recognized commands.
Added delete feature toghether with additional exception handling for the delete feature. Formatted the replies with tabs to make it look nicer.
Updated the Input.txt and EXPECTED.txt because I modified the layout of the replies and also to test the exception handling by inputing some wrong inputs.
